<h3>Priority</h3>
<h5>High School &amp; College</h5>
<p>High School and College students are very active in the Music Ministry of Portland Christian Center. Priority performs in Sunday services throughout the year and presents concerts in the community each season. They are also featured in Portland&rsquo;s Christmas Celebration concerts every December. Priority takes a 10-day music/missions tour every summer. They also are involved in recording projects and community outreach. To sign up,&nbsp;<script type='text/javascript'>var u1015656313='klockaby'; var h706520735='pcctoday.com';var linktext='<b>email</b>';h706520735='pcctoday.com';document.write('<a href=' + 'mail' + 'to:' + u1015656313 + '@' + h706520735 + '>' + linktext + '</a>');
